  body
    div.legal-container
      h1 Privacy Policy for Jinny's Patch Tracker
      p Last Updated: Apr 14, 2026
      
      p Welcome to Jinny's Patch Tracker. Because this is an HRT tracker and journal, we believe your personal and medical information is fundamentally yours. This Privacy Policy explains our absolute commitment to your privacy: we don't want your data, and we don't collect it.
      
      h2 1. Data Collection and Storage
      p Jinny's Patch Tracker is built on a strict, local-only architecture. 
      ul
        li #[strong Zero Server Storage:] We do not operate any databases or servers that store your data. All journal entries, patch logs, and application preferences remain securely on your physical device.
        li #[strong No Accounts:] You do not need to sign in, provide an email, or create an account to use the tracker.
        li #[strong No Developer Access:] We have absolutely no way to see, access, or retrieve your information. What happens on your device stays on your device.
      
      h2 2. Analytics and Advertising
      p We respect your attention and your privacy.
      ul
        li #[strong Ad-Free:] Jinny's Patch Tracker contains zero advertisements. 
        li #[strong No Trackers:] We do not use third-party analytics software, telemetry, or behavioral tracking. We do not sell, rent, or share any information because we don't collect any in the first place.
      
      h2 3. Managing and Deleting Your Data
      p Because your data lives exclusively on your hardware, you retain total control over it. You can permanently delete all your tracking and journal data at any time by:
      ul
        li Clearing the app's local data within your device's operating system settings.
        li Uninstalling the application from your device.
      
      h2 4. Changes to This Policy
      p If we ever change our practices regarding data collection—though our core philosophy is to never collect user data—we will update this policy accordingly. 
      
      h2 Contact Information
      p If you have any questions regarding this privacy policy or the app's architecture, please contact:
      p 
